ber Rider and the Star Sheriffs》\r\n\r\n2069年太阳系的和平受到气化人的破坏，太阳系连邦军为了阻止其侵略行为而展开了战争，最后经历了一场激烈的宇宙大战终于将其击退。历经15年的光阴流逝2084年，飞鹰司令聚集了4位际遇不同的优秀青年驾驶扫荡号对抗卷土重来的气化人。","name":"星銃士ビスマルク","name_cn":"星枪士俾斯麦","tags":[{"name":"TV","count":10,"total_cont":0},{"name":"1984","count":8,"total_cont":0},{"name":"PIERROT","count":6,"total_cont":0},{"name":"萝卜","count":5,"total_cont":0},{"name":"机器人","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"案納正美","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"机战","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"井上和彦","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"日本动画","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"ぴえろ","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"日本","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"robo","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"铳骑士","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"伊東恒久","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"新林実","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"待補1","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"TVA","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"ロボットアニメ","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"无中文字幕","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"80","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"80年代","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"冷门","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"塩屋翼","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"1984年10月","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"原创","count":1,"total_cont":0}],"infobox":[{"key":"中文名","value":"星枪士俾斯麦"},{"key":"别名","value":[{"v":"Star Musketeer Bismarck"},{"v":"Sei jûshi Bisumaruku"}]},{"key":"话数","value":"51"},{"key":"放送开始","value":"1984年10月7日"},{"key":"放送星期","value":"星期日"},{"key":"官方网站","value":"https://pierrot.jp/archive/1980/tv80_09.html"},{"key":"播放电视台","value":"日本テレビ"},{"key":"播放结束","value":"1985年9月29日"},{"key":"导演","value":"案納正美"},{"key":"Copyright","value":"©ぴえろ"},{"key":"企画","value":"鳥海永行"},{"key":"系列监督","value":"鴫野彰"},{"key":"系列构成","value":"馬嶋満"},{"key":"製作","value":"布川ゆうじ"},{"key":"人物设定","value":"加藤茂"},{"key":"机械设定","value":"森木靖泰、デザインオフィスメカマン"},{"key":"imdb_id","value":"tt0294181"}],"rating":{"rank":0,"total":12,"count":{"1":0,"2":0,"3":0,"4":1,"5":2,"6":1,"7":4,"8":4,"9":0,"10":0},"score":6.7},"total_episodes":0,"collection":{"on_hold":7,"dropped":10,"wish":47,"collect":17,"doing":4},"id":29937,"eps":51,"meta_tags":["机战","TV","日本","原创"],"volumes":0,"series":false,"locked":false,"nsfw":false,"type":2},{"date":"1984-10-06","platform":"TV","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/cc/c5/37291_CaeKa.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/cc/c5/37291_CaeKa.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/cc/c5/37291_CaeKa.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/cc/c5/37291_CaeKa.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/cc/c5/37291_CaeKa.jpg"},"summary":"在一个没有战争，所有武器都被禁止的未来，某日，科学狂人基瓦博士将少年麦克的交通机器人强普进行了改造，使其能够巨大化并变形为战斗用机器人伽兰特，而巧合的是这个时候宇宙黑社会的部门之一宇宙不动产对地球发动了侵略，在人们无力抵抗的时候麦克驾驶伽兰特击败了敌人。\r\n战后，基瓦博士撒谎说驾驶伽兰特的是正义的外星人，需要自己作为中介进行联络来欺骗市长等人换取研究经费，并要麦克隐瞒真相继续作战，之后麦克的青梅竹马帕蒂和美少年卡蜜尔也加入了进来，三人一起和邪恶的外星人战斗。","name":"超力ロボ ガラット","name_cn":"超力机器人伽拉特","tags":[{"name":"TV","count":8,"total_cont":0},{"name":"SUNRISE","count":4,"total_cont":0},{"name":"robo","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"1984","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"神田武幸","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"ロボットアニメ","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"星山博之","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"鷹森淑乃","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"サンライズ","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"伊東恒久","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"日本","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"赛璐珞","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"中川勝彦","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"80","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"芦田豊雄","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"旧物","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"日本动画","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"TVA","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"80s","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"平野靖士","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"1984年10月","count":1,"total_cont":0}],"infobox":[{"key":"中文名","value":"超力机器人伽拉特"},{"key":"别名","value":[{"v":"超力机器人伽兰特"}]},{"key":"话数","value":"25"},{"key":"放送开始","value":"1984年10月6日"},{"key":"播放结束","value":"1985年4月6日"},{"key":"企画","value":"日本サンライズ"},{"key":"美术监督","value":"東條俊寿、川名俊英"},{"key":"摄影监督","val